      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like im just spinning my wheels. every time i think i finally have my life together, something happens and i end up right back at zero. same mistakes, same shitty jobs, same people letting me down. it feels like a loop i can't escape no matter how hard i try. im just so tired of starting over.",
